text: Jesús Mansogo Mitogo Obono (born 10 August 1997) is an Equatorial Guinean footballer who plays as a midfielder for Liga Nacional de Fútbol side Cano Sport Academy and the Equatorial Guinea national team. ==International career== Mansogo made his international debut for Equatorial Guinea on 28 July 2019. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Association football midfielders Category:Equatoguinean footballers Category:Equatorial Guinea international footballers Category:Cano Sport Academy players
